p.k: Short France (2012). Hrají: Claudia Tagbo. Režie: Annarita Zambrano.
p.d: In one Paris divided militarily into two like was the former Berlin Est-Ouest, Ines Raymond receives from the right bank people who ask for a visa for the left bank. Each have their reasons and dreams for crossing the Seine, but, Ines must follow the new instructions.
